   143	    "together with a description of the identified or listed hazardous waste involved and, in the "
   144	    "case of a facility referred to in paragraph (1) or (2), a description of the production or "
   145	    "energy recovery activity carried out at the facility and such other information as the "
   146	    "Administrator deems necessary. For purposes of the preceding provisions, the term \"hazardous "
